FBIS3-25753 "drafr039_d_94017" FBIS-AFR-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 SOUTHERN AFRICA Mozambique PRC Vice-Minister of Foreign Affairs Arrives MB2802074994 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network in Portuguese 0400 GMT 28 Feb 94 MB2802074994 Maputo Radio Mozambique Network Language: Portuguese Article Type:BFN [Text] PRC Vice Minister of Foreign Affairs Tian Zengpei said his country hopes a lasting peace will be established in Mozambique through the fulfillment of the General Peace accord signed in Rome. During his stay in Maputo the PRC official will hold talks with Mozambican Government officials and representatives of political parties. Tian Zengpei arrived in Maputo yesterday for a two-day visit at the invitation of Mozambican authorities.
